{"tid":971061,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[退位疑團] 馬來西亞元首點解要退位？","createTime":"2019-01-06T11:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T07:13:42.000Z","uid":53673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d014a6d6db096f8d916ad27f9ff9d634d9e45270","tid":971061,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T11:01:19.000Z","msg":"自元首莫哈末五世被報導結婚後，到呢一刻都冇官方公佈/證實，結婚期間只係話要治療休假，仲搵左霹靂蘇丹署任元首職務<br />\n<br />\n但點解結婚都唔公佈得咁奇怪？同埋點解要講大話隱瞞話要休假治療？莫非條女唔見得光？會影衰馬來西亞？<br />\n<br />\n同埋，點解結完婚要退位？因為要日日扑野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n退位新聞：<a href=\"http://www.orientaldaily.com.my/s/274254\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientaldaily.com.my%2Fs%2F274254&d=BtX1zqEsHkrxBPetBXsbF7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=b8eeddfa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orientaldaily.com.my/s/274254</a><br />\n<br />\n被爆同俄羅斯美女結婚：<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181128/mobile/bkn-20181128170847601-1128_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181128%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181128170847601-1128_00912_001.html&d=BtX1zqEsHkrxBPetBXsbF7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=cce1e518\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181128/mobile/bkn-20181128170847601-1128_00912_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n有圖有真相：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U3pa5Wy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU3pa5Wy.png&h=afdebfa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：東方日報"},{"pid":"1e9cdc56fdf1f7e4c00a00d4ce1a2afe916f34c1","tid":971061,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}